devdoc.details: Educational POC - demonstrates front-running attack on unprotected initialization ATTACK SCENARIO: 1. Contract is deployed 2. Attacker sees deployment in mempool 3. Attacker submits initialize(attackerAddress) with higher gas price 4. Attacker's transaction mines first 5. Attacker becomes admin

params._admin: Address to become the admin DOESN'T protect - Anyone can call this first and steal admin rights

devdoc.title: VulnerableInit
